    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB).  It defines the MIB for monitoring Directory System Agents (DSA), a component of the OSI Directory.  This MIB will be used in conjunction with the APPLICATION-MIB for monitoring DSAs. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
